│ that `Val`, which is the result of `foldExtractFromShuffle`, is expected to be an `ExtractElementInst`.                      │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ Let's look at `foldExtractFromShuffle`.                                                                                      │
│ ```cpp                                                                                                                       │
│ // llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/VectorCombine.cpp                                                                           │
│ static Value *foldExtractFromShuffle(ShuffleVectorInst *SVI,                                                                 │
│                                      ConstantInt *ExtractIdx) {                                                              │
│   // ...                                                                                                                     │
│   int InIdx = SVI->getMaskValue(ExtractIdx->getZExtValue());                                                                 │
│   // ...                                                                                                                     │
