│                                                                                                                              │
│ **4. The Fix**                                                                                                               │
│ The fix is to check if `foldExtractFromShuffle` returned an `ExtractElementInst` before trying to cast and recurse. If it's  │
│ not an `ExtractElementInst`, it must be a simplified constant value, which we can just return directly as it is the final    │
│ result of the chain of extractions.                                                                                          │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ I will modify `translateExtract` in `llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/VectorCombine.cpp`.                                       │
